#: ../new/promotion.rst:64
msgid ""
"The following setting can be used on :tag:`OpenTopped=yes` transports "
"with Initial Payload, which are used to imitate multiple weapons but "
"logically only count as one unit. This works best with "
":tag:`Experience.PromotePassengers=no` and optionally "
":tag:`Experience.FromPassengers=yes`."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/promotion.rst:69
msgid ""
"This does not forward \"experience\" as the ratio of a destroyed object's"
" cost and the own cost. Instead, this forwards the \"rank\" like veteran "
"and elite. A Guardian GI inside a Battle Fortress will always mirror the "
"transport's rank, despite being much cheaper than the vehicle and thus "
"usually promoted earlier."
msgstr ""

